<p>
    Welcome, Program Manager! This dashboard gives you access to reports, claim approvals,
    and tools to oversee the overall claims process in your program.
</p>

<p>
    <strong>View Reports:</strong> Access detailed reports that provide insights into claim
    activities, program performance, and trends across lecturers and coordinators.
</p>

<p>
    <strong>Approve Claims:</strong> Review and approve claims that have already been
    processed by Program Coordinators to ensure compliance and finalize them for payment.
</p>

<p>
    <strong>Logout:</strong> Securely log out of the system once you are finished.
</p>

<hr />

<p>
